    "body": "Also <kbd>Windows Key</kbd> + <kbd>Up Arrow</kbd> (maximize) and <kbd>Windows Key</kbd> + <kbd>Down Arrow</kbd> (unmaximize) doesn't trigger it. Neither does right clicking on the program in the Task Manager and clicking Maximize.\n"
