    "created_at": "2015-08-03T13:30:34Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-08-03T16:02:41Z",
    "body": "There's a discussion on the topic with suggested solutions at : http://stackoverflow.com/questions/9321549/handling-aerosnap-message-in-wndproc\nThey basically say, that Aero Snap doesn't fire the `SC_MAXIMIZE` command and instead we should handle the `WM_SIZE` message or the `WM_WINDOWPOSCHANGING` message, which will fire.\n"
